50|$|International lender of {{last resort}} (ILLR) is a {{facility}} prepared to act when no other lender is capable or willing to lend in sufficient volume to provide or guarantee liquidity in order to avert a sovereign debt crisis or a <b>systemic</b> <b>crisis.</b>|$|E
